00:00:59.280 --> 00:01:09.850
a multimedia producer, a science fiction author,
an arts collaborator, so we have an exceptional

00:01:09.850 --> 00:01:15.350
person here. And her current research is on
architectural design and mythologies about

00:01:15.350 --> 00:01:24.649
new technology. And you've probably heard
